title: IFA Redfish Tour
overview: The IFA Redfish Tour (Inshore Fishing Association) presented by Cabela's recently announced the 2014 tour schedule, complete with 200 percent payback at each event. The schedule includes two regular season events in each of the tour's five divisions and a champion ship event. The IFA Redfish Tourcontinues to draw anglers from Texas to the Carolinas and beyond. Join us for all the excitement on NBCSN.
